Rating: 4
Good recipe - the batter was a bit thick for my liking so I thinned it with regular milk. The pancakes tasted good, but the texture was a bit soft! Almost had the texture of mashed sweet potatoes. Maybe I thinned the batter too much...or maybe I added too much sweet potato (about2 cups worth - it was a big potato!) Regardless, I would make this again. Made a good addition to Thanksgiving weekend brunch.

